al relations position before skyler was named and before he began his job search the company reportedly held discussions with three other individuals to fill the position ny deputy mayor kevin sheekey mayor michael bloombergs political guru  who spearheaded  his shortlived flirtation with a presidential run  who will soon leave city hall for a position at the mayors company bloomberg lp  after mr bloombergs improbable victory in the  mayors race both mr skyler and mr sheekey followed him from his company to city hall since then they have been a part of an enormously influential coterie of advisers howard wolfson the former communications director for hillary clintons presidential campaign and mr bloombergs reelection bid and gary ginsberg now at time warner and formerly at news corporation see alsoedit new york city portal companies portal list of acquired or bankrupt banks in the late s financial crisis list of systemically important banks systemically important financial institution too big to fail list of banks citi orient securities referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j citigroup inc  form k annual report  a b c d e f g h martin mitchell april   citicorp and travelers plan to merge in record  billion deal the new york times   citigroup to spin travelers cnn december     citigroup material legal entities  oneil erin august   the biggest banks in the united states the balance   fortune  fortune magazine   martens pam september   did citigroup defraud billions from abu dhabi saloncom   citigroups  layoffs will impact it newsidgno november     citigroup form k current report filing date nov   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved march     citigroup material legal entities  about citi citi at a glance  primary dealers list federal reserve bank of new york   citis institutional clients group about us  citigroup institutional businesses  citigroup capital markets origination  citigroup icg corporate and investment banking  citigroup markets  securities services  citi research  c