rera francesco april   memo to citi directors wake up on pay the wall street journal subscription required  leising matthew january   citigroup punished for treasury market spoofing by five traders bloomberg lp   citigroup lobbying opensecretsorg retrieved december     citigroup inc summary opensecrets retrieved august     matthew vadum november   liberalism never sleeps retrieved november     a b russ choma december   wall street’s omnibus triumph and others the center for responsible politics retrieved december     gretchen morgenson and andrew martin october   citigroup hires mr inside the new york times retrieved october     lisberg adam march   mayor bloomberg deputy edward skyler says so long to city hall daily news new york retrieved july     barbaro michael march   another exit from bloombergs inner circle the new york times retrieved july    further readingedit schull joseph  years of banking in canada a history of the torontodominion bank by joseph schull illustrated by brad smith vancouver copp clark c ix  p ill  cm langley monica  tearing down the walls new york free press isbn   external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to citigroup official website business data for citigroup inc google finance yahoo finance reuters sec filings links to related articles v t e citigroup brands and companies banamex citibank citibank syariah citigold citi private bank egg metalmark capital red roof inn key people michael e oneill vikram pandit richard parsons william r rhodes lewis b kaden alwaleed bin talal john havens notable former executives winfried bischoff michael bloomberg gary crittenden jamie dimon ahmed fahour stanley fischer lewis glucksman thomas w jones sallie krawcheck victor menezes george s moore samuel osgood joe j plumeri chuck prince john reed robert rubin james stillman rockefeller william rockefeller moses taylor sandy weill robert b willumstad walter wriston corporate directors michael armstrong alain belda george david kenneth t derr 